ent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 4707, \"end\": 4718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999572537, \"rank\": 4.290082672941951e-11, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4528}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4539}, {\"ngram\": \"straightforwardly female athletes\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4577}, {\"ngram\": \"the Court\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4651}, {\"ngram\": \"Arbitration\", \"from\": 4655, \"to\": 4666}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent body\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Lindid notdo so, according to the IBA, while Khelif withdrew her appeal.\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4755, \"end\": 4758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3605993443324885e-11, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Lindid notdo\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4733}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"her appeal\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The process can be costly for athletes.)\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The process\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4805}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In recent years, most controversies over eligibility for women's sports have involved trans athletes.\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4851}, {\"ngram\": \"most controversies\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4871}, {\"ngram\": \"eligibility\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 4888}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 4893, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"trans athletes\", \"from\": 4922, \"to\": 4936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IOC President Thomas Bach dismissed the past week's debate as a \\\"culture war,\\\" which might be true-many newly minted women's-boxing enthusiasts have emerged with strong opinions-but ignores the fact that addressing intersex conditions is an ongoing challenge in women's sports.\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 5215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4938, \"end\": 4951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4952, \"end\": 4963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past week's debate\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 4996}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"culture war\", \"from\": 5000, \"to\": 5014}, {\"ngram\": \"true-many newly minted women's-boxing enthusiasts\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"strong opinions\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5115}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"intersex conditions\", \"from\": 5153, \"to\": 5172}, {\"ngram\": \"an ongoing challenge\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trying to suppress people's questions does not work, and just makes life harder for the athletes involved.\", \"from\": 5216, \"to\": 5322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people's questions\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5253}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5288}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For years, doubts over the South African runner Caster Semenya weredeemedtoberacist, and rival runners who questioned her eligibility in the female category suffered abuse anddeath threats.\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5372, \"end\": 5386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5333}, {\"ngram\": \"doubts\", \"from\": 5335, \"to\": 5341}, {\"ngram\": \"rival runners\", \"from\": 5413, \"to\": 5426}, {\"ngram\": \"her eligibility\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5457}, {\"ngram\": \"the female category\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5480}, {\"ngram\": \"abuse anddeath threats\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet the court's judgment in her case revealed that she was not simply, as she had often beendescribed, a female runner with \\\"naturally high testosterone.\\\"\", \"from\": 5514, \"to\": 5668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court's judgment\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5538}, {\"ngram\": \"her case\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5550}, {\"ngram\": \"a female runner\", \"from\": 5617, \"to\": 5632}, {\"ngram\": \"naturally high testosterone\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had male XY chromosomes anda condition called 5ARD.\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5682, \"end\": 5696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"5ARD\", \"from\": 5719, \"to\": 5723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although genetically male, people with the condition lack a crucial enzyme, 5-alpha reductase, which means that as fetuses, their bodies cannot process a masculinizing hormone calledDHT, which helps determine how the reproductive system develops.\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genetically male\", \"from\": 5735, \"to\": 5751}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5759}, {\"ngram\": \"the condition\", \"from\": 5765, \"to\": 5778}, {\"ngram\": \"a crucial enzyme\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5800}, {\"ngram\": \", 5-alpha reductase\", \"from\": 5800, \"to\": 5819}, {\"ngram\": \"fetuses\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 5848}, {\"ngram\": \"their bodies\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5862}, {\"ngram\": \"a masculinizing hormone calledDHT\", \"from\": 5878, \"to\": 5911}, {\"ngram\": \"the reproductive system\", \"from\": 5939, \"to\": 5962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are therefore born with internal testes but external female genitalia-and thus many are raised as girls.\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 6082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"internal testes\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6017}, {\"ngram\": \"external female genitalia\", \"from\": 6022, \"to\": 6047}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At puberty, their internal testes start to produce adifferentmasculinizing hormone, testosterone, which their bodiesareable to metabolize.\", \"from\": 6083, \"to\": 6221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"puberty\", \"from\": 6086, \"to\": 6093}, {\"ngram\": \"their internal testes\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6116}, {\"ngram\": \"hormone\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6165}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone\", \"from\": 6167, \"to\": 6179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so they develop typically male muscle mass and proportions, and their genitalia take on a more male appearance.\", \"from\": 6222, \"to\": 6337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"typically male muscle mass\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6268}, {\"ngram\": \"proportions\", \"from\": 6273, \"to\": 6284}, {\"ngram\": \"their genitalia\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6305}, {\"ngram\": \"a more male appearance\", \"from\": 6314, \"to\": 6336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At this point, some people with 5ARD feel more comfortable identifying as men rather than as women.\", \"from\": 6338, \"to\": 6437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 6341, \"to\": 6351}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 6353, \"to\": 6364}, {\"ngram\": \"5ARD\", \"from\": 6370, \"to\": 6374}, {\"ngram\": \"more comfortable identifying\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6408}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 6412, \"to\": 6415}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6431, \"to\": 6436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steve Magness: There is good reason for sports to be separated by sex This is why the IOC's insistence that Lin and Khelif were \\\"born as women\\\"-a phrase banned by its own guidelines, but never mind-is unenlightening.\", \"from\": 6439, \"to\": 6656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6526, \"end\": 6529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0715462453697229e-49, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Steve Magness\", \"from\": 6439, \"to\": 6452}, {\"ngram\": \"good reason\", \"from\": 6463, \"to\": 6474}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 6479, \"to\": 6485}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 6505, \"to\": 6508}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 6547, \"to\": 6550}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 6555, \"to\": 6561}, {\"ngram\": \"women\\\"-a phrase\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6591}, {\"ngram\": \"its own guidelines\", \"from\": 6602, \"to\": 6620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With 5ARD, a child can be registered as female at birth, but later develop a significant athletic advantage during puberty from the effects of testosterone.\", \"from\": 6657, \"to\": 6813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"5ARD\", \"from\": 6662, \"to\": 6666}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 6668, \"to\": 6675}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 6707, \"to\": 6712}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant athletic advantage\", \"from\": 6732, \"to\": 6764}, {\"ngram\": \"puberty\", \"from\": 6772, \"to\": 6779}, {\"ngram\": \"the effects\", \"from\": 6785, \"to\": 6796}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone\", \"from\": 6800, \"to\": 6812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some other intersex conditions, such ascomplete androgen insensitivity syndrome, in which a genetically male body iscompletelyunable to process masculinizing hormones in the womb and throughout puberty, provide no edge in sports and so are not a barrier to competing as a female.\", \"from\": 6814, \"to\": 7093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some other intersex conditions\", \"from\": 6814, \"to\": 6844}, {\"ngram\": \"such ascomplete androgen insensitivity syndrome\", \"from\": 6846, \"to\": 6893}, {\"ngram\": \"a genetically male body\", \"from\": 6904, \"to\": 6927}, {\"ngram\": \"hormones\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 6980}, {\"ngram\": \"the womb\", \"from\": 6984, \"to\": 6992}, {\"ngram\": \"puberty\", \"from\": 7008, \"to\": 7015}, {\"ngram\": \"no edge\", \"from\": 7025, \"to\": 7032}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 7036, \"to\": 7042}, {\"ngram\": \"a barrier\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7067}, {\"ngram\": \"a female\", \"from\": 7084, \"to\": 7092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the court ruling, Semenya was asked to reduce her testosterone levels to compete in the female category; she declined.\", \"from\": 7095, \"to\": 7219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court ruling\", \"from\": 7101, \"to\": 7117}, {\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 7119, \"to\": 7126}, {\"ngram\": \"her testosterone levels\", \"from\": 7147, \"to\": 7170}, {\"ngram\": \"the female category\", \"from\": 7185, \"to\": 7204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me I believe if you are a woman, you are a woman,\\\"she saidat the time.\", \"from\": 7220, \"to\": 7295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 7249, \"to\": 7256}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman,\\\"she saidat\", \"from\": 7266, \"to\": 7285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Semenya, who retired from athletics and is raising a young family with her wife, has sincewritten a bookabout how she found the scrutiny over her case humiliating and degrading.\", \"from\": 7296, \"to\": 7473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 7296, \"to\": 7303}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 7322, \"to\": 7331}, {\"ngram\": \"a young family\", \"from\": 7347, \"to\": 7361}, {\"ngram\": \"her wife\", \"from\": 7367, \"to\": 7375}, {\"ngram\": \"a bookabout\", \"from\": 7394, \"to\": 7405}, {\"ngram\": \"the scrutiny\", \"from\": 7420, \"to\": 7432}, {\"ngram\": \"her case\", \"from\": 7438, \"to\": 7446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many athletes subjected toprevious formsof sex verification-which involved genital inspections and even \\\"naked parades\\\"-have said the same.\", \"from\": 7474, \"to\": 7613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many athletes\", \"from\": 7474, \"to\": 7487}, {\"ngram\": \"toprevious formsof sex verification\", \"from\": 7498, \"to\": 7533}, {\"ngram\": \"genital inspections\", \"from\": 7549, \"to\": 7568}, {\"ngram\": \"even \\\"naked parades\\\"-have\", \"from\": 7573, \"to\": 7598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Added to that, many people with 5ARD have no idea of their condition until adolescence, when they are forced to reassess their identity at a profound level.\", \"from\": 7614, \"to\": 7770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 7629, \"to\": 7640}, {\"ngram\": \"5ARD\", \"from\": 7646, \"to\": 7650}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 7656, \"to\": 7663}, {\"ngram\": \"their condition\", \"from\": 7667, \"to\": 7682}, {\"ngram\": \"adolescence\", \"from\": 7689, \"to\": 7700}, {\"ngram\": \"their identity\", \"from\": 7735, \"to\": 7749}, {\"ngram\": \"a profound level\", \"from\": 7753, \"to\": 7769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To have your sense of self challenged like this must be an extraordinarily tough experience-even more so amid a social-media circus.\", \"from\": 7771, \"to\": 7903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sense\", \"from\": 7779, \"to\": 7789}, {\"ngram\": \"self\", \"from\": 7793, \"to\": 7797}, {\"ngram\": \"an extraordinarily tough experience\", \"from\": 7827, \"to\": 7862}, {\"ngram\": \"a social-media circus\", \"from\": 7881, \"to\": 7902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Athletics, the governing body for running, track and field, and related sports, hastightened its rulessince Semenya was competing, as have authorities in other sports-and theIOC defersto them, having scrapped its own sex testingin the 1990s.\", \"from\": 7905, \"to\": 8152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7905, \"end\": 7920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.866343858861068e-36, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the governing body\", \"from\": 7922, \"to\": 7940}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 7954, \"to\": 7959}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"f